    "cwc_problem_agitation_jFJxhg": {
      "type": "CWC_problem_agitation",
      "blocks": {
        "problem_3eHCUM": {
          "type": "problem",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<p>Rising CAC, Flat CVR</p>",
            "text": "<p>Ad costs go up every quarter. Conversion rates stay where they were last year. The math gets worse every month, even when traffic looks the same — and most brands try to solve it by buying more traffic instead of converting more of the traffic they already have.</p><p></p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_new_tab": false
          }
        },
        "problem_UfrhBT": {
          "type": "problem",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<p>Data Everywhere, Answers Nowhere</p>",
            "text": "<p>You've got GA4, Shopify analytics, maybe a heatmap tool and an attribution platform — and somehow still no clear answer on what's actually killing your conversion. Dashboards full of numbers don't tell you which fix matters most. </p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_new_tab": false
          }
        },
        "problem_dYfcpy": {
          "type": "problem",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<p>No One Fully Owns Conversion</p>",
            "text": "<p>Designers make it look right. Devs make it work. Marketers send traffic. The conversion rate sits between all of them and gets owned by no one — which is exactly where most of the revenue leaks happen.</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_new_tab": false
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "problem_3eHCUM",
        "problem_UfrhBT",
        "problem_dYfcpy"
      ],
      "name": "CWC Problem Agitation",
      "settings": {
        "eyebrow": "",
        "heading": "<h2>The 3 Biggest Challenges</h2><h2>Growing DTC Brands Face.</h2>",
        "subtext": "",
        "card_padding": 32,
        "card_radius": 0,
        "bg_color": "#0a0a0a",
        "card_bg": "#ffffff",
        "text_color": "#ffffff",
        "bold_color": "#14a800",
        "rule_color": "#e5e5e0",
