    "cwc_how_we_win_z97xND": {
      "type": "CWC_how_we_win",
      "blocks": {
        "reason_E3UV3P": {
          "type": "reason",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<p>CRO-First, Not Design-First</p>",
            "text": "<p>Every page, section, and test traces back to a metric: conversion rate, AOV, or revenue per visitor. Pretty is a side effect of good CRO — never the starting point.</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_new_tab": false
          }
        },
        "reason_iedxaV": {
          "type": "reason",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<p>Built Mobile-First (Because That's Where The Money Is)</p>",
            "text": "<p>70%+ of DTC traffic is mobile. Most stores still design desktop-first and shrink down. I build mobile-first by default — load speed, tap targets, thumb zones, scroll behavior — all dialed for the device your buyers actually use.</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_new_tab": false
          }
        },
        "reason_HPXHPy": {
          "type": "reason",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<p>Battle-Tested Across 60+ DTC Builds</p>",
            "text": "<p>I'm not starting from a blank canvas every project. Proven page structures, funnel patterns, and section templates — refined across 60+ DTC builds and adapted to your specific offer.</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_new_tab": false
          }
        },
        "reason_mTdUGY": {
          "type": "reason",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<p>Message Matching: Ad → Page → Offer</p>",
            "text": "<p>The ad makes a promise. The page has to keep it. Most stores send paid traffic to a generic homepage or PDP and watch CR die. We match the ad's message to the landing page to the offer — so every click lands somewhere designed for that visitor, not the average one.</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_new_tab": false
          }
        },
        "reason_DyNRDR": {
          "type": "reason",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<p>Positioning & Offer, Not Just Pixels</p>",
            "text": "<p>A great page selling a weak offer still loses. Often the bottleneck isn't the layout — it's how you're positioned against everyone else in the category, and whether the offer itself gives someone a reason to buy. We sharpen your positioning, your USP, and how the offer is framed.</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_new_tab": false
          }
        },
        "reason_grXWp4": {
          "type": "reason",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<p>Designed To Be Tested, Not Just Launched</p>",
            "text": "<p>Conversion isn't a one-shot project. Pages, sections, and funnels are built to be tested and iterated on — clean code, clear hierarchy, easy variants. We keep moving the number after launch, not just at it.</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_new_tab": false
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "reason_E3UV3P",
        "reason_iedxaV",
        "reason_HPXHPy",
        "reason_mTdUGY",
        "reason_DyNRDR",
        "reason_grXWp4"
      ],
      "name": "CWC How We Win",
      "settings": {
        "bg_image": "shopify://shop_images/grid_texture.png",
        "eyebrow": "",
        "heading": "<p>Why Our Approach <strong>Moves The Number </strong>When Others Don't</p>",
        "subtext": "<p>Every project pulls from a proven arsenal — the same CRO strategies, funnel structures, and conversion patterns powering the top DTC brands.</p>",
        "card_padding": 32,
